{"tid":751732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼漢誤闖鱷魚保護區被咬死　村民痛宰292條鱷魚報仇","createTime":"2018-07-22T06:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T07:20:33.000Z","uid":22349,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5f2ba54ec679f1dee21cf10b24b73fe839866255","tid":751732,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:47:24.000Z","msg":"印尼政府西巴布亞省（West Papua）索龍區（Sorong）上周五（13日）有一名村民在採摘蔬菜期間在鱷魚保護區內被咬死，大批憤怒的同鄉為替他報復，竟在隔天屠殺近300條鱷魚，屍體堆積如山，場面駭人。<br />\n<br />\n48歲的蘇吉托為採摘蔬菜，上周五不小心走進一個鱷魚保護區的園地。他被咬後尖叫，園區職員聽到聲音便前來察看，見到鱷魚在攻擊男子。他的葬禮在上周六（14日）舉行。<br />\n<br />\n蘇吉托的親屬和當地居民在他下葬後怒氣沖沖地走當地警局報案。保護區東主見狀已同意賠償，惟數以百計的村民仍大感不滿。他們有的持刀，有的帶着鏟子，闖入園區殺死292條鱷魚，其中一些是只有約10厘米長的幼鱷。官員及警員稱，民眾群情激憤，完全無法阻止他們。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱或會對他們提控。在印尼，殺死受保護動物者會被罰款或判囚入獄。<br />\n<br />\n保護區在2013年獲發執照，園方是為保育而繁殖鹹水鱷（Saltwater Crocodile）及新幾內亞鱷魚，惟同時會屠宰部分動物。"},{"pid":"5ea928ed37ef7d42dd34e7a9acf6df2850fdd495","tid":751732,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1652288/org/4926732bf9b993acb458bd706dae1751.JPG/GDsc6WYjVAvHzCiZUxRqf5tboKBipWjcQNMsoUDTLKE?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1652288%2Forg%2F4926732bf9b993acb458bd706dae1751.JPG%2FGDsc6WYjVAvHzCiZUxRqf5tboKBipWjcQNMsoUDTLKE%3Fv%3Dw800&h=493a3339&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1652354/org/0ee9cf67d66c91362301b4c315b88691.jpg/_GJp7ZNTl9qFK79gP0TjvjZ82tXdQ4H-Rs2sT0bNrE8?v=w800r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1652354%2Forg%2F0ee9cf67d66c91362301b4c315b88691.jpg%2F_GJp7ZNTl9qFK79gP0TjvjZ82tXdQ4H-Rs2sT0bNrE8%3Fv%3Dw800r16_9&h=c5ac0c99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0e24f25bd2aa5e039343945cc180a4a5fc64c7a","tid":751732,"uid":35656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:49:09.000Z","msg":"鱷魚皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cdcf1b86cd5c5c39de130b3b45a660b804c518","tid":751732,"uid":113449,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"咁細條都咬得死，印尼仔真係弱"},{"pid":"b28d68fcad561d5e252e074f0f5fd297ce572cd5","tid":751732,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03cdcf1b86cd5c5c39de130b3b45a660b804c518","tid":751732,"uid":113449,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"咁細條都咬得死，印尼仔真係弱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eea5c0880610e22e88d6722e53117804739237f","tid":751732,"uid":150098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03cdcf1b86cd5c5c39de130b3b45a660b804c518","tid":751732,"uid":113449,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"咁細條都咬得死，印尼仔真係弱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:54:46.000Z","msg":"如果過百條呢？"},{"pid":"a9cafa8a779cd2078babb35029a5dc5caa694e2b","tid":751732,"uid":5460,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"03cdcf1b86cd5c5c39de130b3b45a660b804c518","tid":751732,"uid":113449,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"咁細條都咬得死，印尼仔真係弱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:56:05.000Z","msg":"好似你咁 有個 keyboard 揸手就可以打天下"},{"pid":"cace29e7db392560666cb10a2fe0b093d3d78c8d","tid":751732,"uid":81671,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:57:52.000Z","msg":"明明係自己on9走入鱷魚保護區"},{"pid":"f875552b11a5ae9242218d2bea3742f1c0b645f8","tid":751732,"uid":51578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:07:45.000Z","msg":"屌你自己行去比人食<br />\n報咩撚野仇?"},{"pid":"b540d38282aaf2e7966dff47543ca58d5bcb90b0","tid":751732,"uid":61512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:09:55.000Z","msg":"低等人種"},{"pid":